  Restricting jython

  20 Feb 2012; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> pyclamav-0.4.1-r1.ebuild:
  Restricting pypy #404033

  30 Jun 2010; Arfrever Frehtes Taifersar Arahesis <arfrever@gentoo.org>
